description: Planning to visit Union City, California? or living there? This skill would give an overview of the city. It can also give you the top 5 things to do with their address. Also you can ask for the local news.
exampleInteractions: Alexa Ask Union City Guide about top attractions
Alexa Ask Union City Guide what is the top 5 things to do
name: Union City Guide
shortDescription: Get top attractions list or local news about Union City, California
